text:
Katie Holmes won’t take any more of Jamie Foxx’s bad habits! RadarOnline.com has learned the health-conscious actress told her junk food-loving boyfriend that his obsession with fatty snacks has got to go.

“When she first started dating Jamie, he made it seem like he was healthy, too, and a nature lover,” an insider told RadarOnline.com. “The truth soon came out – he’s a candy bar-eating closet junkie.”

Meanwhile, Holmes, 39, is the epitome of good health, and works hard to keep her thin frame. She is a big fan of cycling and yoga, and has even run in the New York City Marathon.
title: Diet Dilemma! Katie Holmes Demands Jamie Foxx Give Up Junk Food
